# Keep the build context lean and deterministic. Dependencies are installed
# fresh inside the image (pnpm for web, cargo for api), so local artifacts must
# never leak in and clobber the in-image, target-platform installs.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
apps/api/target
**/target
.git
.gitignore
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
**/.env
**/.env.*
*.md
